### 1. \'c1\'e0\'e7\'ee\'e2\'fb\'e9 \'f8\'e0\'e1\'eb\'ee\'ed \'e8\'e3\'f0\'fb (Game Loop)\par
\'ca\'e0\'e6\'e4\'e0\'ff \'e8\'e3\'f0\'e0 \'ed\'e0 Pygame \'f1\'f2\'f0\'ee\'e8\'f2\'f1\'ff \'ed\'e0 \'fd\'f2\'ee\'ec \'f4\'f3\'ed\'e4\'e0\'ec\'e5\'ed\'f2\'e5: \'e8\'ed\'e8\'f6\'e8\'e0\'eb\'e8\'e7\'e0\'f6\'e8\'ff, \'f6\'e8\'ea\'eb (\'ee\'e1\'f0\'e0\'e1\'ee\'f2\'ea\'e0 \'f1\'ee\'e1\'fb\'f2\'e8\'e9 -> \'ee\'e1\'ed\'ee\'e2\'eb\'e5\'ed\'e8\'e5 \'eb\'ee\'e3\'e8\'ea\'e8 -> \'ee\'f2\'f0\'e8\'f1\'ee\'e2\'ea\'e0), \'e7\'e0\'e2\'e5\'f0\'f8\'e5\'ed\'e8\'e5.\par
\par
```python\par
import pygame\par
import sys\par
\par
pygame.init()\par
screen = pygame.display.set_mode((800, 600))\par
pygame.display.set_caption("\'cc\'ee\'ff \'f1\'f3\'ef\'e5\'f0 \'e8\'e3\'f0\'e0")\par
clock = pygame.time.Clock()\par
\par
running = True\par
while running:\par
    # 1. \'ce\'c1\'d0\'c0\'c1\'ce\'d2\'ca\'c0 \'d1\'ce\'c1\'db\'d2\'c8\'c9 (\'ed\'e0\'e6\'e0\'f2\'e8\'ff \'ee\'e4\'e8\'ed \'f0\'e0\'e7, \'e7\'e0\'ea\'f0\'fb\'f2\'e8\'e5 \'ee\'ea\'ed\'e0)\par
    for event in pygame.event.get():\par
        if event.type == pygame.QUIT:\par
            running = False\par
            \par
    # 2. \'ce\'c1\'cd\'ce\'c2\'cb\'c5\'cd\'c8\'c5 \'cb\'ce\'c3\'c8\'ca\'c8 (\'e4\'e2\'e8\'e6\'e5\'ed\'e8\'e5, \'f4\'e8\'e7\'e8\'ea\'e0)\par
    dt = clock.tick(60) / 1000.0  # \'c4\'e5\'eb\'fc\'f2\'e0-\'e2\'f0\'e5\'ec\'ff \'e4\'eb\'ff \'ed\'e5\'e7\'e0\'e2\'e8\'f1\'e8\'ec\'ee\'e3\'ee \'ee\'f2 FPS \'e4\'e2\'e8\'e6\'e5\'ed\'e8\'ff\par
    \par
    # 3. \'ce\'d2\'d0\'c8\'d1\'ce\'c2\'ca\'c0 (\'d4\'ee\'ed -> \'ce\'e1\'fa\'e5\'ea\'f2\'fb -> \'c8\'ed\'f2\'e5\'f0\'f4\'e5\'e9\'f1)\par
    screen.fill("black")  # \'c2 Pygame-CE \'ec\'ee\'e6\'ed\'ee \'ef\'e8\'f1\'e0\'f2\'fc \'ed\'e0\'e7\'e2\'e0\'ed\'e8\'ff \'f6\'e2\'e5\'f2\'ee\'e2 \'f1\'f2\'f0\'ee\'ea\'ee\'e9!\par
    \par
    # ... \'e7\'e4\'e5\'f1\'fc \'f4\'f3\'ed\'ea\'f6\'e8\'e8 \'ee\'f2\'f0\'e8\'f1\'ee\'e2\'ea\'e8 ...\par
\par
    pygame.display.flip() # \'cf\'ee\'ea\'e0\'e7\'fb\'e2\'e0\'e5\'ec \'ed\'ee\'e2\'fb\'e9 \'ea\'e0\'e4\'f0\par
\par
pygame.quit()\par
sys.exit()\par
```\par
\par
---\par
\par
### 2. \'ca\'ee\'ee\'f0\'e4\'e8\'ed\'e0\'f2\'fb, Rect \'e8 FRect (\'ca\'eb\'fe\'f7\'e5\'e2\'e0\'ff \'ea\'ee\'ed\'f6\'e5\'ef\'f6\'e8\'ff!)\par
\'c2 Pygame \'e2\'f1\'b8 \'ef\'f0\'ff\'ec\'ee\'f3\'e3\'ee\'eb\'fc\'ed\'ee\'e5. **Rect** \'f5\'f0\'e0\'ed\'e8\'f2 \'ea\'ee\'ee\'f0\'e4\'e8\'ed\'e0\'f2\'fb \'e8 \'f0\'e0\'e7\'ec\'e5\'f0\'fb. \'c2 Pygame-CE \'e4\'ee\'e1\'e0\'e2\'e8\'eb\'e8 **FRect** (Float Rect) \f1\emdash  \f0\'ee\'ed \'ef\'ee\'e4\'e4\'e5\'f0\'e6\'e8\'e2\'e0\'e5\'f2 \'e4\'f0\'ee\'e1\'ed\'fb\'e5 \'f7\'e8\'f1\'eb\'e0, \'f7\'f2\'ee \'e4\'e5\'eb\'e0\'e5\'f2 \'e4\'e2\'e8\'e6\'e5\'ed\'e8\'e5 \'e8\'e4\'e5\'e0\'eb\'fc\'ed\'ee \'ef\'eb\'e0\'e2\'ed\'fb\'ec.\par
\par
```python\par
# \'d1\'ee\'e7\'e4\'e0\'ed\'e8\'e5: (x, y, \'f8\'e8\'f0\'e8\'ed\'e0, \'e2\'fb\'f1\'ee\'f2\'e0)\par
player_rect = pygame.FRect(100.5, 200.2, 50, 50)\par
\par
# \'cf\'ee\'eb\'e5\'e7\'ed\'fb\'e5 \'f2\'ee\'f7\'ea\'e8 \'ef\'f0\'e8\'e2\'ff\'e7\'ea\'e8 (\'ec\'ee\'e6\'ed\'ee \'f7\'e8\'f2\'e0\'f2\'fc \'e8 \'e8\'e7\'ec\'e5\'ed\'ff\'f2\'fc):\par
player_rect.x, player_rect.y         # \'c2\'e5\'f0\'f5\'ed\'e8\'e9 \'eb\'e5\'e2\'fb\'e9 \'f3\'e3\'ee\'eb\par
player_rect.centerx, player_rect.centery # \'d6\'e5\'ed\'f2\'f0\par
player_rect.center                   # \'ca\'ee\'f0\'f2\'e5\'e6 (x, y) \'f6\'e5\'ed\'f2\'f0\'e0\par
player_rect.top, player_rect.bottom  # \'c2\'e5\'f0\'f5\'ed\'ff\'ff \'e8 \'ed\'e8\'e6\'ed\'ff\'ff \'e3\'f0\'e0\'ed\'e8\par
player_rect.left, player_rect.right  # \'cb\'e5\'e2\'e0\'ff \'e8 \'ef\'f0\'e0\'e2\'e0\'ff \'e3\'f0\'e0\'ed\'e8\par
\par
# \'cf\'e5\'f0\'e5\'ec\'e5\'f9\'e5\'ed\'e8\'e5 \'ef\'f0\'ff\'ec\'ee\'f3\'e3\'ee\'eb\'fc\'ed\'e8\'ea\'e0\par
player_rect.x += 150 * dt  # \'c4\'e2\'e8\'e6\'e5\'ed\'e8\'e5 \'e2\'ef\'f0\'e0\'e2\'ee \'ed\'e0 150 \'ef\'e8\'ea\'f1\'e5\'eb\'e5\'e9 \'e2 \'f1\'e5\'ea\'f3\'ed\'e4\'f3\par
```\par
\par
---\par
