**\'c0. \'ca\'eb\'e0\'e2\'e8\'e0\'f2\'f3\'f0\'e0 (\'c7\'e0\'e6\'e0\'f2\'e8\'e5 \'ea\'ed\'ee\'ef\'ee\'ea \f1\emdash  \f0\'e4\'eb\'ff \'f5\'ee\'e4\'fc\'e1\'fb)**\par
\'cf\'e8\'f8\'e5\'f2\'f1\'ff \'e2 \'e3\'eb\'e0\'e2\'ed\'ee\'ec \'f6\'e8\'ea\'eb\'e5 *\'e2\'ed\'e5* `for event in pygame.event.get()`:\par
